  "riddle": "1. To begin your journey, seek the scientist who seamlessly marries biology and machines, crafting flows of vital fluids. How many offspring does this pioneering mind claim?\n\n2. From there, delve into the legacy of a revered educational institution in the Empire State, once shepherded by the engineer from clue 1. What year was this bastion of learning established?\n\n3. Ascend to new heights: calculate how many meters above the sea the scholarly grounds of this institution stand.\n\n4. How well-beloved is this place of academia, according to the wisdom of the digital crowd? Seek their aggregated endorsement score.\n\n5. Weave together the wisdom of altitudes and crowdsourced acclaim: In steps 3 and 4, find the numerical harmony between these two.\n\n6. Return to antiquity with a temporal twist. Transform the founding year uncovered in clue 2 into ancient script—how many letters does the numeral hold?\n\n7. Journey now to the borough known for its bridges and brownstones. Tell me, what summit does the elevation chart reveal?\n\n8. Look closer at this borough’s swells and dips. How high does it rise, according to the maps of today?\n\n9. Count the sacred centers within proximity to this bustling borough, where peace and contemplation meet modern life.\n\n10. Unite your findings from clues 8 and 9—what result emerges when the borough’s peak joins its spiritual havens?\n\n11. Peer through the lens of mathematics and find the largest prime that divides the peak revealed in clue 7.\n\n12. Turn your gaze west without leaving this borough's embrace. According to online voices, how many stars grace its reputation?\n\n13. When one thinks of states in stars and stripes, they wonder: how many citizens call this land their own?\n\n14. Venture to the grand gallery housed along a tree-lined parkway. How many inns can be found nearby to house the curious traveler or the weary art enthusiast?\n\n15. To conclude this journey, let numerical magic ensue: Compute the digital root of the sum from clues 4, 7, 9, and 10. This final single digit unlocks the path to your answer.",
